
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Account Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #000000;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #f5a300;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    p {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: white !important;
    }

    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .logo img {
      width: 100px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #f5a300;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-info p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .contact-info a {
      color: aqua;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://<%= websiteLink %>/img/maillogo.png" alt=" <%= websiteName %> Logo">
    </div>
    
    <h1>Account Verification</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= username %>,</p>
    <br>Your documents has been submitted for verification.
        <br>Please kindly wait for our verification department to review your documents.
        <br>You will be notified shortly.
        
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please feel free to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:<%= websiteSupportMail %>"><%= websiteSupportMail %></a>.</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing <%= websiteName %>!</p>
    <p>
      <a class="button" href="<%= websiteLink %>">Visit <%= websiteName %></a>
    </p>
    <div>
      <p>Email: <%= websiteSupportMail %></p>
      <p>Website: <%= websiteLink %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>